Use cases ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


            New Volume
                |
---------------------------------------
   |                        |
   |                        |
   v                        v
Password               Use key files
   |                        |
   |--> Token pass          |---> Add Token Files
   v                        v
Normal pass           Add file(s)/path





----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Mount procedure ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


|user password |   KDF   | header encryption key | Decrypt Header | Master primary key   | Decr Volume
|keyfile(s)    |-------> | header secondary key  | -------------> | Master secondary key |-------------> 
|header salt   |         |                       |                |                      |





